msgstr "出口接口"

msgid "Steer the naive -> server connection out of this interface. Empty = use the global default egress interface."
msgstr "将 naive → 服务器的连接从该接口发出。留空则使用全局默认出口接口。"

msgid "(use global default)"
msgstr "（使用全局默认）"

