msgstr "自动更新"

msgid "Periodic update is enabled when global_rules.geosite_update = 1 (cron, default 04:30 daily). Toggle it and the auto-update minute on the Basic Settings page (future)."
msgstr "当 global_rules.geosite_update = 1 时启用定期更新（cron，默认每日 04:30）。后续可在“基本设置”页切换并调整自动更新时间。"

