msgstr "生成并预览"

msgid "(none)"
msgstr "（无）"

msgid "Click to generate/preview."
msgstr "点击生成/预览。"

msgid "(system default route)"
msgstr "（系统默认路由）"

msgid "Routing rules consumed by BypassCore (the split/routing engine) and shared with the nftables/ipset plane. domain_list and ip_list use v2ray rule prefixes: geosite:, geoip:, domain:, full:, regexp:, ext:, or bare CIDR/domain."
msgstr "由 BypassCore（分流/路由引擎）消费、并与 nftables/ipset 平面共享的路由规则。domain_list 与 ip_list 使用 v2ray 规则前缀：geosite:、geoip:、domain:、full:、regexp:、ext: 或裸 CIDR/域名。"

msgid "Install the Linux ELF from https://github.com/kinmeic/BypassCore/releases (the routing/split engine). Route-test / resolve / observatory auto-disable if missing or not a Linux ELF."
msgstr "从 https://github.com/kinmeic/BypassCore/releases 下载安装 Linux ELF（分流/路由引擎）。缺失或非 Linux ELF 时，路由测试 / DNS 解析 / Observatory 自动禁用。"

msgid "BypassCore route test"
msgstr "BypassCore 路由测试"

msgid "Preview which shunt rule / outbound a destination matches, using the BypassCore routing engine. Requires the BypassCore Linux ELF binary."
msgstr "用 BypassCore 路由引擎预览某目的地命中哪条分流规则 / 出站。需要 BypassCore 的 Linux ELF 二进制。"

msgid "The config generated from your shunt rules and fed to BypassCore (the routing engine). Traffic itself is carried by naiveproxy."
msgstr "由你的分流规则生成、供 BypassCore（路由引擎）使用的配置。流量本身由 naiveproxy 转发。"


msgid "DNS resolve (BypassCore)"
msgstr "DNS 解析（BypassCore）"

msgid "Resolve a domain via BypassCore's DNS subsystem (the split-DNS engine; ChinaDNS-NG remains the live resolver)."
msgstr "通过 BypassCore 的 DNS 子系统解析域名（分流 DNS 引擎；ChinaDNS-NG 仍作为实时解析器）。"

msgid "Enter a domain to resolve."
msgstr "请输入要解析的域名。"

msgid "Resolve"
msgstr "解析"

msgid "Resolved IPs appear here."
msgstr "解析到的 IP 显示在此。"

msgid "BypassCore domestic DNS"
msgstr "BypassCore 国内 DNS"

msgid "Upstream for domestic domains in the BypassCore DNS section (UDP/TCP/DoT/DoH). Leave empty to disable the split (only the remote upstream is emitted)."
msgstr "BypassCore DNS 段中用于国内域名的上游（UDP/TCP/DoT/DoH）。留空则禁用分流（只输出远程上游）。"

msgid "BypassCore remote DNS"
msgstr "BypassCore 远程 DNS"

msgid "Upstream for everything else in the BypassCore DNS section."
msgstr "BypassCore DNS 段中用于其余所有域名的上游。"

msgid "Domestic split domain"
msgstr "国内分流域名"

msgid "v2ray rule prefix that selects which domains use the domestic upstream (default geosite:cn)."
msgstr "v2ray 规则前缀，决定哪些域名使用国内上游（默认 geosite:cn）。"

msgid "BypassCore as transparent core"
msgstr "BypassCore 作为透明代理核心"

msgid "0 (default): naiveproxy carries traffic, BypassCore is diagnostic-only. 1: BypassCore runs -run as the transparent proxy core (inbound + sniff + route + SOCKS5-to-naiveproxy); naiveproxy becomes its SOCKS upstream. Requires BypassCore with the SOCKS5 dialer + UDP TPROXY listener (commit e60bd1f+)."
msgstr "0（默认）：naiveproxy 承载流量，BypassCore 仅做诊断。1：BypassCore 以 -run 作为透明代理核心（inbound + sniff + route + SOCKS5 拨到 naiveproxy），naiveproxy 降为它的 SOCK 上游。需要带 SOCKS5 拨号器 + UDP TPROXY listener 的 BypassCore（commit e60bd1f+）。"

msgid "Force Proxy LAN IP"
msgstr "强制代理局域网 IP"

msgid "When enabled, the proxy uses the LAN IP as the source address for proxied connections from LAN clients."
msgstr "启用后，代理将使用局域网 IP 作为来自局域网客户端的代理连接的源地址。"

msgid "Enable auto update rules"
msgstr "启用自动更新规则"

msgid "Enable scheduled automatic update of GeoIP/Geosite rule files."
msgstr "启用后按计划自动更新 GeoIP/Geosite 规则文件。"

msgid "Shunt Rule List"
msgstr "分流规则列表"

msgid "Domain/IP Query"
msgstr "域名/IP 查询"

msgid "Enter a domain or IP to query the Geo rule list they belong to."
msgstr "输入域名或 IP，查询其所属的 Geo 规则列表。"

msgid "Enter a domain or IP"
msgstr "请输入域名或 IP"

msgid "By entering a domain or IP, you can query the Geo rule list they belong to."
msgstr "输入域名或 IP，可查询其所属的 Geo 规则列表。"

msgid "By entering a GeoIP or Geosite, you can extract the domains/IPs they contain."
msgstr "输入 GeoIP 或 Geosite，可提取其包含的域名/IP。"

msgid "Use the GeoIP/Geosite query function to verify if the entered Geo rules are correct."
msgstr "使用 GeoIP/Geosite 查询功能验证输入的 Geo 规则是否正确。"

msgid "No results were found!"
msgstr "未找到结果！"
